Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:38.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:49.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:53.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:03:00.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:06.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:25.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with Trafalgar Law and \Nhave come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the detail of the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:31.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,nightmare that Dressrosa faced\N10 years ago is revealed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the rightful king of this country!\NAnd now, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sell you this country\Nfor 10 billion berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please let me borrow all of your money!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Don't make me do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:04:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}, please stop!\N--What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy... What kind of king he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the night has just begun, soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should dance, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Parasite String!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NM-My arm is moving on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it move on its own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it what's happening to King-{\i1}sama{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way to justify myself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This country is finished!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doflamingo set us up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!\NCan we do it already, Doffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. Don't rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make the people tremble\Nwith fear more
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get them hate King Riku\Nwith all their heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the heroes will appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Nightmare!\NThe Tragic Night of Dressrosa!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What happened to King-{\i1}sama{\i0}?!\N--The whole country is in chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't look right\Nwhen he left the palace earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't expect this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more than we can handle within \Nthe country so I called the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Vergo said\Nhe's gonna take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:07:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monet! What are you doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a maid!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you opening the gate of the palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Viola.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use your Clairvoyance,\Nyou can see clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what is happening in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting to welcome\Nthe new royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The east tower has been bombed!\N--Some pirates have breached the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took Viola-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The palace is not too bad.\NIt's kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I love it-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect for Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop, you fools!\N--Are you Doflamingo's clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monet! Let go of Viola-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys do something to King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we have a lot to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to "clean up" the whole palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing such a thing?!\NKing Riku Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
