Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did we do something wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were always just.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the king we were proud of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You told us that you needed our money.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we've brought you all our money.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you've...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...always cared about us\Nmore than anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you were our pride and joy!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku has...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku has trampled\Non our feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna take our money\Nand kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To satisfy his own selfish desires,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's gonna toss us aside like trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a low-down, dirty scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King Riku Army's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, move out of there! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to save this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Don Quixote Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?\NWhy are the pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're gonna save us\Nfrom the King Riku Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like how you "dance"!\NKing Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trebol! Pica! Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go and sweep out the trash\Nfrom the whole country!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo! Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo! Doflamingo! Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow your doom! Embrace violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop running! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive your evil family!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go to hell already, Rebecca!\N--Chop her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're a piece of shit!\N--Drop dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The country fell into hands of Doflamingo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nin just one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How awful!\NIt's like a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cunning of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I can't stand that Doflamingo guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believed that King Riku \Nwent crazy at that time, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we got in touch with \Nthe new king Doflamingo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so ashamed of myself\Nfor distrusting King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! It's really too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let the innocent king that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you all admired so much die for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo loved the special ability\Nthe former princess Viola-{\i1}sama{\i0} had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she bargained with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you promise me that\Nyou won't kill my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will obey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She still lives and works\Nunder Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming an officer in his group
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and changing her name to Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-She's an officer?!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, King Riku is still \Nalive thanks to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sure he's still living somewhere\Nin this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't imagine how much pain
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he must've gone through over the last decade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how hard it must've been for Viola-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear, anger, tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:18:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how she has spent\Nthe last decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, on the same night,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,other soldiers were \Nmanipulated as the king was
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and massacred the civilians unwillingly,\Nthey must've been suffering so much, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought all of them must've\Nbeen killed that night!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some got killed\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but others surrendered to Doflamingo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're working for him as his guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sold out to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe they made an agonizing choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just followed the crazy king's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for welcoming them\Nto work under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, I can't help crying!\NEverybody has been suffering so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tragedy! You poor people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:19:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were soldiers who got killed\Nand who surrendered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you sum it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't add up to a \Nwhole army for a country!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I have lost some memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost some memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fra-land.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what I've told you earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after we became toys,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we remember everything\Nabout when we were humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But people around us, even our own family,\Nforgot that we even existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even know\Nthat they lost their loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the biggest tragedy of Dressrosa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even we toys forgot some things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, there might be your \Nfriends among those toys
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that are walking on the streets
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can't recognize them\Nbecause you forgot about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, they must've been feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,angry since Doflamingo turned them into toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it all!\NWhy should I be a toy?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get away from my wife!\NDamn! I can't say what I wanna say!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--Damn Doflamingo!\N--I hate him so much!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't there anybody\Nwho can take him down?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo tried to bury all the dissidents
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are countless dissidents\Ndwelling in the shadows of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That unknown number of those poor people\Nis the key to our plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you think \Nthere is a chance to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that it seems foolhardy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto fight the Warlord's group but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if all the toys in this country are dissidents,\Nit'd be a powerful enough force!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you're going for\Ntaking down Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're only here to destroy the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's done, we'll say \Ngoodbye to the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so mad at Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're destined to fight\Nthis decisive battle today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the event of this morning,\Nthey're challenging us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a coincidence\Nthat Usoland came to us today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody from above is telling us\Nto fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--What event?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo's abdication\Nfrom the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the fact is we...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you imagine how happy we were\Nwhen we heard about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we heard it was a false report.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We felt like we were dropped\Nfrom heaven to the edge of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was only natural for us to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...decide to fight him today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're so sorry for what we did!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're retired but you led your crew here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no disciples\Nto succeed the Happo Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had a grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's not so easy to be a pirate, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe it's just my imagination\Nbut I feel like I'm forgetting something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt the same way 10 years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, hey, hey, hey, where am I going?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandpa, help me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What have they done to me -\NAbdullah, the lone wolf?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What have they done to me -\NJeet, the maverick warrior!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Crest Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was gonna show me \Nthe way but he's collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:22:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Zoro really here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.15,0:23:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Kin'emon!
